            <abstract>Professional papers of Bergen Davis (1869-1958) Professor of Physics, Columbia
                University, 1903-1939 (A.M., 190ffl; Ph.D. 1901;DD.Sc. 1929) containing
                correspondence, manuscripts, photographs, memorabilia and printed
